    <title type="html"><![CDATA[山寨一个微博按钮]]></title>
    <link href="http://wenatuhs.github.com/blog/2012/06/06/shan-zhai-yi-ge-wei-bo-an-niu/"/>
    <updated>2012-06-06T01:36:00+08:00</updated>
